# SmartLauncher Public Release

SmartLauncher is an Android launcher project focused on intelligent home screen app arrangement. This public repository contains a sanitized version of the project that is suitable for open-source publication and review.

This repository is published by Mildred Reyes Petisme.

Contact:
mildredreyespetisme@yahoo.com

Included in this public release:
- Android app source code
- Gradle project files
- Public-facing documentation

Excluded from this public release:
- Signing keys and keystores
- Local signing configuration
- Private product documents
- Local build artifacts and machine-specific files

For project setup and usage details, see the main README in this repository.
